\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Must contain at least ONE non-obvious observation (something the reader's team probably hasn't flagged)\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Must end with a clear statement of what's at stake: the dollar magnitude, the time window, or the structural shift\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Tone: confident, direct, analytical. Not breathless or promotional. The insight should speak for itself.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
